*sil-gentium-5.000 (07 Mar 2015)

  07 Mar 2015; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> +sil-gentium-5.000.ebuild:
  version bump

  21 Oct 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> sil-gentium-1.508.ebuild:
  Marked ~x64-macos, bug #486818

  27 May 2012; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> -sil-gentium-1.0.2.ebuild,
  sil-gentium-1.508.ebuild:
  Mark 1.508 stable. Remove old.

*sil-gentium-1.508 (08 Jan 2012)

  08 Jan 2012; Ryan Hill <dirtyepic@gentoo.org> +sil-gentium-1.508.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Version bump. Switch to using Gentium Plus for Opentype and Graphite
  features such as correct diacritics and alternates, as well as expanded glyph
  coverage.

  14 Jun 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> sil-gentium-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Marked ~x86-macos (#369547) and ~ppc-macos

  06 Apr 2009; Christian Faulhammer <fauli@gentoo.org>
  -sil-gentium-1.0.1.ebuild:
  clean up

  06 Apr 2009; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> sil-gentium-1.0.2.ebuild:
  s390/sh stable

  19 Mar 2009; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> sil-gentium-1.0.2.ebuild:
  stable ppc, bug 256159

  13 Feb 2009; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> sil-gentium-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Re-add ~s390/~sh

  06 Feb 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> sil-gentium-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #256159).

